    <section id="about" class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>About the Gender Gap</h2>
                <p>Understanding the challenges and the importance of equality.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-content">
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="assets/about-image.jpg" alt="Infographic showing gender equality statistics">
                </div>
                <div class="about-text">
                    <p>The gender gap represents the disparities between men and women in various aspects of life, including economic participation, education, health, and political empowerment. Addressing this gap is crucial for social justice, economic growth, and overall societal well-being.</p>
                    <p>Our organization is dedicated to raising awareness, implementing impactful initiatives, and providing resources to help bridge this gap. We believe in a future where everyone has equal opportunities to thrive, regardless of their gender.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Promoting equal access to education and employment.</li>
                        <li>Advocating for fair policies and legislation.</li>
                        <li>Empowering women and girls through mentorship and skill development.</li>
                        <li>Fostering inclusive and respectful environments.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

